    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Kamaka excavata Ariyama, 2007, male (A – C) and female (D – H): A, pleopod 1; B, pleopod 2; C, pleopod 3; D, gnathopod 2; E – H, oostegites of gnathopod 2 – pereopod 5." ;
